  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1.\u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd. \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "QR in Yali. Court sale",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the national pass for fuel is about to be implemented, they are making the pass like an identity card and a 'key tag' and charging for it.",
        "A person in Yali is QR. The code is made in the form of a key tag so that it can be stuck in the vehicle openings. For that he donates 600 rupees.",
        "Similarly, another person uses QR as an identity card. Designs the line. For that he is given 300 rupees. (a)"
      ],
